text.tspan: Graph Drawing Contest 2021 · Ammer David · Korpitsch Thorsten · Pointner Simon

tspan.tspan: Images of movies are accessed from IMDB. Movie reel and camera
background from svgsilh.com. The movie data is provided by the 29th
International Symposium on Graph Drawing and Network Visualization.
Movie order is optimized with a meta heuristic approach, in detail simulated annealing. The cost is defined as
of the same director, from their centroid. This will optimally result in a minimum
number of crossings between movies directed by the
same director. The original graph is rendered with D3,
while further adjustments are performed using Inkscape.
